    {
      "widget_id": "gy5p9hx4",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Optimiser vos <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">opérations</em> de services professionnels.",
      "en": "Optimize your professional services <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">operations</em>."
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "jc3y9v2l",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Au cœur d'un cabinet performant se trouvent une gestion fluide de l'information, une coordination efficace et une sécurité sans faille des données clients. Nous vous aidons à mettre en place les outils adaptés.</p>",
      "en": "<p>At the heart of a high-performing firm lie seamless information management, efficient coordination, and rock-solid client data security. We help you put the right tools in place.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "t7i5nuyi",
      "type": "html",
      "field": "html",
      "fr": "<span class=\"kv-badge\">◆ Outils de collaboration & design</span>",
      "en": "<span class=\"kv-badge\">◆ Collaboration & design tools</span>"
    },
    {
