    },
    {
      "widget_id": "8edunvc9",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Vos défis <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">quotidiens</em>",
      "en": "Your daily <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">challenges</em>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "xz5nkcps",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Informations clients dispersées",
      "en": "Scattered client information"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "uha6iv07",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Les données sont éparpillées entre fichiers locaux, courriels et outils non connectés, rendant leur centralisation difficile.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Data is scattered across local files, emails, and disconnected tools, making centralization difficult.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "2fpredfo",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Sécurité & confidentialité",
      "en": "Security & confidentiality"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "qmghimxa",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Partage non contrôlé de fichiers sensibles, mots de passe faibles, accès mal cadrés : vos données clients sont exposées.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Uncontrolled sharing of sensitive files, weak passwords, poorly scoped access: your client data is exposed.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "lc4fmjtn",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Suivi projet & livrables",
      "en": "Project & deliverables tracking"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "phcejxl4",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Sans outil structurant, les échéances, les statuts et les versions de documents deviennent opaques.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Without a structuring tool, deadlines, statuses, and document versions become opaque.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "vvs8gcgk",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Collaboration interdisciplinaire",
      "en": "Cross-team collaboration"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "l1b8wxs6",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Les échanges entre équipes (ingénierie, gestion, commercial) souffrent de silos et de doublons.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Exchanges between teams (engineering, management, sales) suffer from silos and duplication.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "buluo2za",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Capitalisation du savoir",
      "en": "Knowledge capitalization"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "k8v4amb0",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Le savoir-faire reste dans la tête de quelques experts et se perd à chaque départ ou réorganisation.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Know-how stays in the heads of a few experts and is lost with every departure or reorganization.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "8gctc4si",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Conformité réglementaire",
      "en": "Regulatory compliance"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "aau4ro2q",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Traçabilité, archivage légal, RGPD : sans cadre clair, le risque de non-conformité grimpe.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Traceability, legal archiving, GDPR: without a clear framework, the risk of non-compliance climbs.</p>"
    },
